title: Tetris (the best I've found)
description:
This is a flash version of Tetris I found a long time ago and forgot about. Recently rediscovered in archived files, It's the best version I've played on a computer.

No installation required. It's runs within its own container. Just place anywhere and launch.

Absolutely clean. I installed this on my mothers computer.

This should run on anything with flash installed but hasn't been tested on the most modern operating systems.

Drag to re-size game as desired. Not locked into any resolution.  


You can enable special block patterns in options but the game always starts with default block patterns that everyone is familiar with.

My best score is 8120 with default blocks. Good luck
